Class BaseMailArchiveService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.message.impl.BaseMessageService
      • org.sakaiproject.mailarchive.impl.BaseMailArchiveService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContextObserver, EntityProducer, EntitySummary, MailArchiveService, CacheRefresher, MessageService, StorageUser
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DbMailArchiveService

    public abstract class BaseMailArchiveService
extends BaseMessageService
implements MailArchiveService, ContextObserver

    BaseMailArchiveService extends the BaseMessageService for the specifics of MailArchive.
